answers.answer: High iron content can cause this, as well as vitamin B. Urinary tract infection and kidney infections can also cause this.Yes, it's true.Vitamins can cause this problem. Your body safeguards itself by expelling unused portions of vitamins in your body.I am 7 months pregnant and use vitamin B to help ease the nausea.It works,but within an hour or so I have the smelliest urine and it is very dark.Another culprit is diabetes/hypoglycemia...ask your doctor to test you for this.

What other tests should I be doing?
title: Orange Spots in Urine
